All right.

786
01:34:32.473 --> 01:34:33.993
Are you sure you don't
wanna have some?

787
01:34:34.017 --> 01:34:38.062
I won't. thank you.
And then leave it to mash.

788
01:34:38.187 --> 01:34:41.190
I will.
I will. definitely will.

789
01:34:41.274 --> 01:34:43.484
Uh... What are you working on?

790
01:34:43.568 --> 01:34:45.403
It's a gauntlet

791
01:34:45.528 --> 01:34:49.324
lined with specialized
polymer solar cells.

792
01:34:49.407 --> 01:34:51.826
- Wow.
- Here. let me show you.

793
01:34:51.868 --> 01:34:55.079
We borrowed this from
the Kryptonian scout ship.

794
01:34:56.581 --> 01:34:57.999
Oh. maybe you should. uh...

795
01:34:58.082 --> 01:34:59.709
a fraction.
Thank you. thank you.

796
01:34:59.792 --> 01:35:00.835
Of course.

797
01:35:06.007 --> 01:35:07.592
Ah.

798
01:35:07.717 --> 01:35:10.720
Ah. now. let's see how that did.

799
01:35:10.803 --> 01:35:13.222
Ha! Yes.

800
01:35:13.347 --> 01:35:14.891
Not to be sneezed at.

801
01:35:14.974 --> 01:35:17.518
A gauntlet that captures
and dissipates energy.

802
01:35:17.602 --> 01:35:19.395
It's Master Wayne's idea.

803
01:35:19.479 --> 01:35:21.731
Maybe you should work
on a lasso. too?

804
01:35:21.814 --> 01:35:24.692
- In black. of course.
- Oh.

805
01:35:31.449 --> 01:35:34.619
All right. Victor Stone.

806
01:35:50.676 --> 01:35:53.137
Something is not working.

807
01:35:53.262 --> 01:35:54.931
Mmm.

808
01:36:04.524 --> 01:36:06.984
Looks like you have a date.
Miss Prince.

809
01:37:03.875 --> 01:37:07.211
Why are you looking
for me. Diana?

810
01:37:07.336 --> 01:37:08.629
You know who I am.

811
01:37:08.713 --> 01:37:10.965
I know more than you
can possibly imagine.

812
01:37:11.048 --> 01:37:14.302
Then maybe you already know
I need your help.

813
01:37:14.427 --> 01:37:15.636
The world does.

814
01:37:16.721 --> 01:37:18.681
Fuck the world.

815
01:37:20.057 --> 01:37:22.685
You've obviously
been through a great deal.

816
01:37:23.728 --> 01:37:26.814
I can't begin to imagine what.

817
01:37:26.856 --> 01:37:30.485
But whatever happened to you.
you have gifts now.

818
01:37:30.568 --> 01:37:32.403
Gifts?

819
01:37:32.528 --> 01:37:34.697
What part of this
looks like a gift to you?

820
01:37:34.780 --> 01:37:36.532
We need you. Victor.

821
01:37:36.657 --> 01:37:38.367
And maybe you need us.

822
01:37:38.451 --> 01:37:40.161
I don't need anyone.

823
01:37:42.371 --> 01:37:43.539
Not anymore.

824
01:37:43.623 --> 01:37:46.083
I told myself the same
for a long time.

825
01:37:52.757 --> 01:37:55.718
I lost someone I loved once.

826
01:37:58.471 --> 01:38:03.226
I shut myself off from everyone.

827
01:38:04.810 --> 01:38:07.730
But I had to learn
to open back up again.

828
01:38:10.149 --> 01:38:13.736
The truth is.
I'm still working on it.

829
01:38:13.819 --> 01:38:17.782
And if you asked to meet me...

830
01:38:17.907 --> 01:38:20.826
you're working on it. too.

831
01:39:32.231 --> 01:39:34.442
You were right
about the metal sample

832
01:39:34.483 --> 01:39:36.027
from the Superman ship.

833
01:39:36.152 --> 01:39:39.614
When we bombard it with X-rays
from the electron-laser.

834
01:39:39.739 --> 01:39:41.324
look what happens.

835
01:39:50.374 --> 01:39:52.126
3.5 million kelvin.

836
01:39:52.168 --> 01:39:55.421
The inner core of the metal
becomes superheated.

837
01:39:55.546 --> 01:39:57.965
Hot. dense matter.

838
01:40:01.052 --> 01:40:03.888
You're looking at
the hottest thing on Earth.

839
01:40:04.013 --> 01:40:06.349
Exact words I said
to my prom date.

840
01:40:06.432 --> 01:40:08.059
She dumped me anyway.

841
01:40:08.184 --> 01:40:09.310
Yeah.

842
01:40:13.522 --> 01:40:14.648
Hey. Doc.

843
01:40:14.732 --> 01:40:16.317
do you think Batman is connected

844
01:40:16.359 --> 01:40:19.153
to the object
the CID is looking for?

845
01:40:20.071 --> 01:40:23.324
You know. 6-1-9-8-2?

846
01:40:24.492 --> 01:40:25.701
No...

847
01:40:26.535 --> 01:40:27.870
I don't.

848
01:41:02.613 --> 01:41:04.824
Oh. Victor.

849
01:41:21.799 --> 01:41:23.884
All right! Let's go!

850
01:41:24.969 --> 01:41:26.303
Commissioner Gordon?

851
01:41:26.429 --> 01:41:27.471
Come on!

852
01:41:27.596 --> 01:41:28.764
Your messages.

853
01:41:28.889 --> 01:41:30.349
Hey. hey!

854
01:41:33.102 --> 01:41:35.604
Don't have to see the sky
to know it's a full moon.

855
01:41:35.730 --> 01:41:38.816
{\an5}Half of Gotham's
reality-challenged
community showed up.

856
01:41:38.941 --> 01:41:41.110
Say they saw flying monsters
by the harbor.

857
01:41:41.193 --> 01:41:43.195
You were right. Ma.
Police Academy.

858
01:41:43.320 --> 01:41:45.156
What's wrong with dental school?

859
01:41:48.075 --> 01:41:51.162
"Attacked by
a flying vampire."

860
01:41:51.287 --> 01:41:54.498
"Looked like a giant bat
with huge fangs."

861
01:41:54.623 --> 01:41:56.292
On a possibly related note.

862
01:41:56.375 --> 01:41:58.794
sketch of the suspect
in the abductions

863
01:41:58.919 --> 01:42:00.421
at the lab across the harbor.

864
01:42:00.504 --> 01:42:03.632
{\an5}- Looks like...
- I know what it looks like. Crispus.

865
01:42:03.799 --> 01:42:06.385
Come on. you think he fights
criminals for 20 years here

866
01:42:06.510 --> 01:42:09.388
and then he goes to Metropolis
and kidnaps eight people?

867
01:42:10.473 --> 01:42:11.557
I'll talk to him tonight.

868
01:42:11.682 --> 01:42:13.267
How. Jim?

869
01:42:13.392 --> 01:42:14.977
How do you think?

870
01:42:33.037 --> 01:42:34.455
Silas?

871
01:42:34.580 --> 01:42:35.789
Hey. hey.

872
01:42:35.873 --> 01:42:37.333
Hey. hey!

873
01:42:41.795 --> 01:42:44.340
- Oh. my goodness.
- Where's the cyborg?

874
01:42:44.465 --> 01:42:45.508
His name is Victor.

875
01:42:46.425 --> 01:42:49.178
We met. spoke.

876
01:42:50.012 --> 01:42:52.014
Give him time.

877
01:42:52.181 --> 01:42:54.183
You must be Barry. I'm Diana.

878
01:42:54.266 --> 01:42:58.062
Hi. Barry. I'm Diana.
That's not right. Great.

879
01:42:58.187 --> 01:43:00.523
- So. this is us.
- Yeah. this is us.

880
01:43:00.648 --> 01:43:01.982
Oh!

881
01:43:02.066 --> 01:43:04.860
Awesome! It's the Bat-Signal.
That's your...

882
01:43:04.944 --> 01:43:07.029
- Oh. sorry.
- That's your signal.

883
01:43:07.154 --> 01:43:08.614
That means we have to go now.

884
01:43:08.739 --> 01:43:12.451
- Yeah. that's what that means.
- It's so cool.

885
01:44:09.592 --> 01:44:11.343
Commander Mera. I told the king

886
01:44:11.468 --> 01:44:13.220
the perimeter guards were taken.

887
01:44:13.304 --> 01:44:14.847
He won't send reinforcements.

888
01:44:14.972 --> 01:44:17.558
He says all the reserves are
needed in the rebel regions.

889
01:44:17.683 --> 01:44:22.146
He's as shortsighted
as he is cruel.

890
01:44:22.271 --> 01:44:23.939
All right. take what men
we have left

891
01:44:24.064 --> 01:44:25.774
and form a phalanx
around the Mother Box.

892
01:46:05.708 --> 01:46:07.710
You can't escape.

893
01:46:08.585 --> 01:46:10.546
I'm not trying to.

894
01:48:12.876 --> 01:48:15.212
Vulko told me you would come.

895
01:48:15.337 --> 01:48:18.257
The firstborn
of beloved Queen Atlanna.

896
01:48:20.843 --> 01:48:22.177
Wait.

897
01:48:24.054 --> 01:48:25.264
Please.

898
01:48:28.809 --> 01:48:30.227
I knew her.

899
01:48:32.271 --> 01:48:34.565
Well. that makes one of us.

900
01:48:34.690 --> 01:48:36.525
My parents died in the wars.

901
01:48:38.235 --> 01:48:39.820
She took me in.

902
01:48:39.903 --> 01:48:41.572
What a saint.

903
01:48:41.697 --> 01:48:43.824
You dare speak
of Queen Atlanna that way?

904
01:48:43.907 --> 01:48:46.660
Your queen left me
on my father's doorstep

905
01:48:46.743 --> 01:48:48.495
and never gave me
another thought.

906
01:48:48.537 --> 01:48:51.748
Your mother left you
to save your life.

907
01:48:51.874 --> 01:48:54.585
You cannot imagine
how it hurt her.

908
01:48:56.044 --> 01:48:58.255
What it cost her.

909
01:48:59.298 --> 01:49:01.633
But you're not
a defenseless child now.

910
01:49:03.802 --> 01:49:05.512
It would have been
her responsibility

911
01:49:05.554 --> 01:49:08.891
to follow that monster
to the surface and stop him.

912
01:49:09.558 --> 01:49:10.642
Now.

913
01:49:11.935 --> 01:49:13.353
it's yours.

914
01:50:17.626 --> 01:50:18.961
Yes.

915
01:50:42.025 --> 01:50:43.276
<i>Steppenwolf.</i>

916
01:50:43.402 --> 01:50:45.362
tell me what you've learned.

917
01:50:45.487 --> 01:50:47.990
Two boxes found and awake.

918
01:50:48.156 --> 01:50:51.159
With the combined power
of the two Mother Boxes.

919
01:50:51.243 --> 01:50:54.496
I've been able to finish
the stronghold's defenses.

920
01:50:54.579 --> 01:50:57.124
Where is the third Mother Box?

921
01:50:57.207 --> 01:50:59.626
The parademons
sense its presence

922
01:50:59.668 --> 01:51:01.378
and search for the third.

923
01:51:01.503 --> 01:51:02.504
They have taken prisoners

924
01:51:02.629 --> 01:51:04.840
who carry its scent.

925
01:51:05.674 --> 01:51:07.301
Go.

926
01:51:07.384 --> 01:51:09.511
Interrogate the prisoners.

927
01:51:10.178 --> 01:51:12.014
Find the third.

928
01:51:13.515 --> 01:51:15.809
They will tell me
what they know.

929
01:51:16.852 --> 01:51:19.604
or I will rip it from them.

930
01:52:02.731 --> 01:52:04.524
How many of you are there?

931
01:52:05.275 --> 01:52:06.526
Not enough.

932
01:52:08.236 --> 01:52:10.655
Dozens of witnesses
all over Gotham.

933
01:52:10.781 --> 01:52:12.157
Description matches the suspect

934
01:52:12.282 --> 01:52:14.076
in the Metropolis abductions.

935
01:52:14.201 --> 01:52:15.369
Parademons.

936
01:52:15.911 --> 01:52:17.245
Okay.

937
01:52:17.412 --> 01:52:19.623
The demons must have caught
the scent of a Mother Box.

938
01:52:19.748 --> 01:52:21.124
At the lab.

939
01:52:21.249 --> 01:52:23.377
They carried people away
to find out what they know.

940
01:52:23.460 --> 01:52:24.562
So the eight may still be alive.

941
01:52:24.586 --> 01:52:25.587
Nine.

942
01:52:25.712 --> 01:52:27.589
Oh.

943
01:52:27.672 --> 01:52:30.425
The head of STARLABS
was taken tonight.

944
01:52:35.430 --> 01:52:38.100
Wow. okay.
So. another scientist.

945
01:52:38.225 --> 01:52:39.476
So. how do we find him?

946
01:52:39.601 --> 01:52:41.144
There must be a nest nearby.

947
01:52:41.269 --> 01:52:45.565
I plotted all the sightings
in Metropolis. Gotham.

948
01:52:45.649 --> 01:52:47.776
No discernable pattern
I can see.

949
01:52:47.901 --> 01:52:49.361
The lines on the map
don't converge.

950
01:52:49.486 --> 01:52:50.779
On land.

951
01:52:50.904 --> 01:52:52.322
These lead back
to Stryker's Island.

952
01:52:52.447 --> 01:52:53.573
between the two cities.

953
01:52:53.657 --> 01:52:54.741
These are air vents.

954
01:52:54.866 --> 01:52:56.326
They all lead down to the tunnel

955
01:52:56.451 --> 01:52:58.620
to a Metropolis project
that was abandoned in '29.

956
01:52:58.787 --> 01:53:00.956
The nest could be there.

957
01:53:01.081 --> 01:53:03.041
Uh. is he coming with us now.

958
01:53:03.166 --> 01:53:05.127
because we're not all
gonna fit in your car.

959
01:53:05.252 --> 01:53:06.711
I have something bigger.

960
01:53:07.838 --> 01:53:10.715
Do you really think that...

961
01:53:10.841 --> 01:53:14.428
Oh. wow. they just...
They really just vanish. huh?

962
01:53:14.469 --> 01:53:17.055
Oh. That's rude.

963
01:53:55.677 --> 01:53:57.721
We're close.

964
01:53:57.846 --> 01:54:00.015
The scent of the enemy.

965
01:54:00.640 --> 01:54:01.892
Of absence.

966
01:54:02.392 --> 01:54:04.019
Darkness.

967
01:54:04.644 --> 01:54:06.021
Death.

968
01:54:06.188 --> 01:54:07.230
Where are we. Alfred?

969
01:54:07.355 --> 01:54:08.523
<i>Stryker's Island.</i>

970
01:54:08.607 --> 01:54:10.650
You should be directly under

971
01:54:10.734 --> 01:54:13.528
the venting tower
for the tunnel.

972
01:54:13.612 --> 01:54:14.988
<i>Now look to your left.</i>

973
01:54:15.071 --> 01:54:17.032
<i>you'll see a staircase
to the machine room.</i>

974
01:54:17.115 --> 01:54:19.701
<i>Thermal scan shows
a cluster of people there.</i>

975
01:54:19.826 --> 01:54:21.161
That's it.

976
01:54:21.286 --> 01:54:22.662
Let's go.

977
01:54:36.468 --> 01:54:39.221
Right.
Is there... Is there a plan?

978
01:54:40.722 --> 01:54:41.973
Either of you?

979
01:54:42.098 --> 01:54:44.142
Don't engage alone.

980
01:54:44.267 --> 01:54:45.560
We do this together.

981
01:54:54.444 --> 01:54:56.238
I heard about you.

982
01:54:57.948 --> 01:54:59.532
Didn't think you were real.

983
01:54:59.616 --> 01:55:01.201
I'm real when it's useful.

984
01:55:11.294 --> 01:55:13.046
I grow tired of your silence.

985
01:55:13.171 --> 01:55:15.548
Now tell me.
where is the Mother Box?

986
01:55:22.430 --> 01:55:24.599
Please. We have families.

987
01:55:24.724 --> 01:55:26.977
Then you have weakness.

988
01:55:27.102 --> 01:55:28.478
Steppenwolf.

989
01:55:28.603 --> 01:55:32.941
Okay. I'm guessing
that's the bad guy.

990
01:55:33.108 --> 01:55:34.276
Good guess.

991
01:55:34.401 --> 01:55:38.154
I'm really. really missing
Superman right now.

992
01:55:38.280 --> 01:55:40.240
Circle to the other side.

993
01:55:40.323 --> 01:55:42.701
We'll surround them
and surprise him.

994
01:55:46.997 --> 01:55:49.124
You have been near a Mother Box.

995
01:55:49.207 --> 01:55:50.792
The scent is on you.

996
01:55:50.917 --> 01:55:52.460
I don't know
what you're talking about.

997
01:55:52.627 --> 01:55:54.462
- Where is it?
- Leave him alone!

998
01:55:54.629 --> 01:55:56.965
He... He doesn't know.

999
01:56:00.510 --> 01:56:02.304
Wait. please. please!

1000
01:56:07.726 --> 01:56:10.770
You carry
the scent. too. But stronger.

1001
01:56:10.854 --> 01:56:13.148
I will die before I tell you.

1002
01:56:13.315 --> 01:56:15.358
You'll die if you don't.

1003
01:56:15.483 --> 01:56:16.651
No!

1004
01:56:25.744 --> 01:56:26.828
Victor.

1005
01:56:26.953 --> 01:56:28.330
Kill them both.

1006
01:56:31.833 --> 01:56:34.294
Ah. Amazon.

1007
01:56:34.377 --> 01:56:37.047
But not like your sisters.

1008
01:56:37.172 --> 01:56:38.298
Stronger.

1009
01:57:09.329 --> 01:57:11.664
Amazon.

1010
01:57:14.042 --> 01:57:15.543
Hold!

1011
01:57:15.669 --> 01:57:17.962
This one will be mine.

1012
01:57:19.798 --> 01:57:22.300
I belong to no one.

1013
01:57:36.106 --> 01:57:38.316
Guys. this is not together.

1014
01:57:45.156 --> 01:57:46.574
Help get those people
out of here.

1015
01:57:46.700 --> 01:57:48.868
I'll make sure these things
follow me.

1016
01:57:58.753 --> 01:58:00.255
Everybody. move!

1017
01:58:08.888 --> 01:58:10.432
A little quicker.

1018
01:58:12.767 --> 01:58:14.060
- Are you good?
- Yeah.

1019
01:58:14.185 --> 01:58:16.938
I've got this. Keep moving.

1020
01:58:18.773 --> 01:58:19.773
This way.

1021
01:58:56.060 --> 01:58:57.645
The energy is dissipating.

1022
01:58:57.729 --> 01:59:00.231
<i>My gauntlet worked!</i>

1023
01:59:00.356 --> 01:59:02.817
Celebrate later. Alfred.
I need the Nightcrawler.

1024
01:59:02.901 --> 01:59:04.986
Thought you'd never ask.

1025
01:59:05.069 --> 01:59:07.322
Crawler's on the way.
Initiating remote mode.

1026
01:59:37.519 --> 01:59:38.519
Thank you. Alfred.

1027
01:59:38.603 --> 01:59:39.854
Don't mention it.

1028
02:00:02.710 --> 02:00:03.878
No!

1029
02:00:07.423 --> 02:00:08.424
Whew.

1030
02:00:11.553 --> 02:00:13.137
They're safe.
Get back to the tunnel.

1031
02:00:13.263 --> 02:00:16.599
Tunnel. Right.
Aliens. bad guy. sword lady.

1032
02:00:28.361 --> 02:00:29.571
My turn.

1033
02:01:51.736 --> 02:01:53.404
Catastrophic failure
of all systems.

1034
02:01:53.529 --> 02:01:56.074
Are you all right. Master Wayne?

1035
02:01:56.199 --> 02:01:57.325
Are you all right?

1036
02:02:07.710 --> 02:02:11.506
You have the blood
of the old gods in you.

1037
02:02:25.770 --> 02:02:26.980
You okay?

1038
02:02:27.480 --> 02:02:28.690
Mm.

1039
02:02:28.815 --> 02:02:30.483
Wasn't sure you'd come.

1040
02:02:31.526 --> 02:02:32.735
You're my father.

1041
02:02:36.364 --> 02:02:37.365
Go.

1042
02:02:50.878 --> 02:02:52.046
No!

1043
02:03:37.300 --> 02:03:39.761
Relax. Alfred.
I'll take it from here.

1044
02:03:41.262 --> 02:03:43.264
Uh. do I know you?

1045
02:04:14.045 --> 02:04:15.379
What are we under. right now?

1046
02:04:16.047 --> 02:04:17.423
Gotham Harbor.

1047
02:04:56.045 --> 02:04:57.421
Who is that?

1048
02:05:22.697 --> 02:05:23.865
Come on.

1049
02:05:28.995 --> 02:05:30.288
Diana. get on!

1050
02:06:32.099 --> 02:06:33.643
What is it?

1051
02:06:41.275 --> 02:06:42.818
Show me.

1052
02:07:22.024 --> 02:07:23.651
It is here.

1053
02:07:24.318 --> 02:07:27.446
On this world.

1054
02:08:01.188 --> 02:08:02.508
Sir. you're gonna
be in quarantine

1055
02:08:02.606 --> 02:08:03.983
for possible alien microbes.

1056
02:08:04.066 --> 02:08:05.860
U.S. government protocols
require that...

1057
02:08:05.985 --> 02:08:08.988
I know the requirements.
I wrote them.

1058
02:08:13.451 --> 02:08:14.952
It called to him.

1059
02:08:15.077 --> 02:08:16.495
The Mother Box.

1060
02:08:16.579 --> 02:08:18.080
The one he already has.

1061
02:08:18.205 --> 02:08:21.417
He has two. He took
the Mother Box from Atlantis.

1062
02:08:21.542 --> 02:08:24.045
All he needs now
is the lost Box of Men.

1063
02:08:24.128 --> 02:08:25.421
If he doesn't already have it.

1064
02:08:28.966 --> 02:08:30.509
He doesn't have it.

1065
02:08:33.512 --> 02:08:34.805
I do.

1066
02:08:45.232 --> 02:08:47.360
Have you finished the conquest?

1067
02:08:47.443 --> 02:08:48.694
Not yet. DeSaad.

1068
02:08:48.778 --> 02:08:51.238
Then why do you summon me?

1069
02:08:51.364 --> 02:08:52.865
I bring news.

1070
02:08:52.990 --> 02:08:55.993
Before mighty Darkseid
came to the throne.

1071
02:08:56.118 --> 02:09:01.290
he searched the universe
for the ultimate weapon.

1072
02:09:01.415 --> 02:09:03.542
The Anti-Life Equation.

1073
02:09:03.626 --> 02:09:05.711
The key to controlling all life

1074
02:09:05.753 --> 02:09:08.255
and all will
throughout the multiverse.

1075
02:09:08.339 --> 02:09:11.592
{\an5}He found it hidden on a
primitive planet. but before...

1076
02:09:11.675 --> 02:09:14.553
The story of the defiance
is well-known.

1077
02:09:14.678 --> 02:09:17.348
I have found
the primitive planet.

1078
02:09:17.473 --> 02:09:19.475
The world that fought back.

1079
02:09:19.600 --> 02:09:21.560
It is Earth.

1080
02:09:21.602 --> 02:09:23.854
The Anti-Life Equation is carved

1081
02:09:23.979 --> 02:09:28.025
into the surface
of this very world.

1082
02:09:31.612 --> 02:09:33.155
Are you certain?

1083
02:09:33.280 --> 02:09:34.323
I have seen it.

1084
02:09:34.448 --> 02:09:37.660
I have looked with my own eyes.

1085
02:09:39.411 --> 02:09:40.413
{\an5}Anti-Life.

1086
02:10:21.203 --> 02:10:22.872
My lord.

1087
02:10:24.331 --> 02:10:28.210
Oh. Steppenwolf.

1088
02:10:28.335 --> 02:10:32.506
My lord. I am
but your humble servant.

1089
02:10:32.590 --> 02:10:35.468
Can it be true
that you have found it?

1090
02:10:35.551 --> 02:10:38.387
I have. great one.

1091
02:10:38.512 --> 02:10:41.473
The lost world is Earth.

1092
02:10:41.599 --> 02:10:45.811
Anti-Life is here.

1093
02:10:45.853 --> 02:10:49.190
If it is redemption you seek.
find the third box.

1094
02:10:49.315 --> 02:10:52.485
{\an5}synchronize The Unity. and
when this world is scorched.

1095
02:10:52.568 --> 02:10:55.946
I will come for my great prize.

1096
02:10:56.697 --> 02:10:59.867
You will come to Earth?

1097
02:10:59.950 --> 02:11:04.371
I have turned
100.000 worlds to dust

1098
02:11:04.496 --> 02:11:05.915
looking for Anti-Life.

1099
02:11:06.040 --> 02:11:09.418
Looking for those
who robbed me of my glory.

1100
02:11:09.543 --> 02:11:12.713
I will stride across their bones

1101
02:11:12.796 --> 02:11:15.382
and bask in the glow
of Anti-Life.

1102
02:11:15.466 --> 02:11:18.260
And all of existence

1103
02:11:18.385 --> 02:11:21.680
shall be mine.

1104
02:11:25.226 --> 02:11:29.188
It shall be so. my master.

1105
02:11:33.400 --> 02:11:35.027
So cool.

1106
02:11:35.110 --> 02:11:38.072
{\an5}From the outside. it looks like
this building was abandoned.

1107
02:11:41.492 --> 02:11:43.244
It wants to fly.

1108
02:11:44.453 --> 02:11:46.455
You talk to machines?

1109
02:11:46.580 --> 02:11:48.624
I speak to intelligence.

1110
02:11:48.749 --> 02:11:49.976
This one's saying she can't fly

1111
02:11:50.000 --> 02:11:51.627
because of a software issue.

1112
02:11:51.752 --> 02:11:53.879
but I could fix it
with a little time.

1113
02:12:03.347 --> 02:12:05.891
There's a dark spot
in my data stream.

1114
02:12:05.975 --> 02:12:08.435
I could feel
the other two boxes.

1115
02:12:08.519 --> 02:12:10.396
I know they're awake.

1116
02:12:10.479 --> 02:12:12.022
but I can't see where they are.

1117
02:12:12.147 --> 02:12:14.307
Well. we can't attack unless
we know where the base is.

1118
02:12:14.400 --> 02:12:16.443
Even if we knew.

1119
02:12:16.527 --> 02:12:19.780
I've never seen a being
as strong as Steppenwolf.

1120
02:12:21.782 --> 02:12:23.158
Maybe one.

1121
02:12:23.284 --> 02:12:25.703
Hmm. Superman.

1122
02:12:25.828 --> 02:12:27.496
As long as
the third box is asleep.

1123
02:12:27.621 --> 02:12:29.873
they can't see it.
only sense it.

1124
02:12:29.999 --> 02:12:32.251
We need to keep moving
so they can't catch up.

1125
02:12:32.334 --> 02:12:33.752
No. That's just a strategy

1126
02:12:33.877 --> 02:12:35.838
to lose more slowly. not to win.

1127
02:12:35.963 --> 02:12:38.799
Remind me. are flamethrowers
not a thing?

1128
02:12:38.882 --> 02:12:40.042
Why don't we just destroy it?

1129
02:12:40.092 --> 02:12:42.177
Fire doesn't destroy the boxes.

1130
02:12:42.303 --> 02:12:44.221
They're an unknown form
of matter.

1131
02:12:44.346 --> 02:12:45.597
Oh. they love heat.

1132
02:12:45.639 --> 02:12:47.808
They absorb it.
hold it in their cores.

1133
02:12:47.933 --> 02:12:50.602
Well. you know
a lot about these boxes.

1134
02:12:50.644 --> 02:12:51.937
Makes you think.

1135
02:12:52.021 --> 02:12:54.648
Where'd you find the box.
Victor?

1136
02:12:54.773 --> 02:12:56.442
Are you trying to say something?

1137
02:12:56.525 --> 02:12:58.277
Oh. I'm saying it.

1138
02:12:58.360 --> 02:13:00.654
How do we know you're not
working for them?

1139
02:13:02.364 --> 02:13:04.408
It's a long story.

1140
02:13:04.533 --> 02:13:06.368
You got somewhere else to be?

1141
02:13:13.751 --> 02:13:15.210
The Nazis found the box

1142
02:13:15.336 --> 02:13:17.671
at the end
of the Second World War.

1143
02:13:17.755 --> 02:13:20.841
buried under
an Italian monastery.

1144
02:13:20.924 --> 02:13:23.260
The Allies intercepted it
on its way to Hitler.

1145
02:13:23.385 --> 02:13:26.305
They brought it back
to the States in '44.

1146
02:13:26.347 --> 02:13:30.642
Unknown object 6-1-9-8-2.

1147
02:13:30.684 --> 02:13:32.561
It collected dust
in the Pentagon archives

1148
02:13:32.686 --> 02:13:34.438
for 70 years

1149
02:13:34.563 --> 02:13:38.067
till DoD began to study
the Superman ship.

1150
02:13:39.360 --> 02:13:41.862
A researcher at STARLABS
made a connection

1151
02:13:41.945 --> 02:13:43.113
between the ship...

1152
02:13:44.365 --> 02:13:46.367
and 6-1-9-8-2.

1153
02:13:46.533 --> 02:13:50.204
He understood they were
both alien technologies.

1154
02:13:50.329 --> 02:13:52.373
Different civilizations.

1155
02:13:52.456 --> 02:13:55.501
similar properties.

1156
02:13:55.584 --> 02:13:59.004
And though the box had slept
for thousands of years.

1157
02:13:59.129 --> 02:14:02.591
the researcher formulated
a theory on how to awaken it.

1158
02:14:02.716 --> 02:14:04.718
And so did.

1159
02:14:06.762 --> 02:14:07.930
Then...

1160
02:14:09.890 --> 02:14:12.935
I had an accident
that should've killed me.

1161
02:14:13.060 --> 02:14:16.271
But in an act of desperation
or madness.

1162
02:14:16.397 --> 02:14:18.982
the researcher harnessed
the power of the Mother Box.

1163
02:14:34.957 --> 02:14:37.042
He unleashed an alien technology

1164
02:14:37.167 --> 02:14:39.962
he didn't fully understand.

1165
02:14:40.087 --> 02:14:42.756
He used that power
to keep me alive.

1166
02:14:46.260 --> 02:14:48.053
Alive...

1167
02:14:48.095 --> 02:14:50.264
but turned into this.

1168
02:14:52.933 --> 02:14:55.352
The box went back to sleep

1169
02:14:56.103 --> 02:14:58.021
and he never returned it.

1170
02:15:00.357 --> 02:15:02.776
That researcher was Silas Stone.

1171
02:15:04.361 --> 02:15:06.029
My father.

1172
02:15:09.283 --> 02:15:10.909
Wait.

1173
02:15:10.993 --> 02:15:14.288
your father saved your life
with one of these things?

1174
02:15:14.455 --> 02:15:16.790
Aren't they
psycho murder machines?

1175
02:15:16.957 --> 02:15:19.251
They're change machines.

1176
02:15:19.334 --> 02:15:22.504
The boxes don't think in terms
of healing or killing.

1177
02:15:22.629 --> 02:15:24.548
alive or dead.

1178
02:15:24.673 --> 02:15:27.092
They rearrange matter
at the will of their masters.

1179
02:15:27.134 --> 02:15:28.886
regenerate. reinstate.

1180
02:15:29.011 --> 02:15:30.429
Reinstate?

1181
02:15:30.554 --> 02:15:31.972
A box has the power

1182
02:15:32.055 --> 02:15:33.974
to reinstate anterior
particle relationships.

1183
02:15:34.141 --> 02:15:36.021
So. you mean in the way
that particles of matter

1184
02:15:36.101 --> 02:15:37.301
can't be created or destroyed.

1185
02:15:37.352 --> 02:15:39.354
their relations just transform.

1186
02:15:39.480 --> 02:15:42.316
Burn down a house.
the particles still exist.

1187
02:15:42.399 --> 02:15:44.985
Particles of house
become particles of smoke.

1188
02:15:45.110 --> 02:15:49.323
Anybody with a match
can turn a house to smoke.

1189
02:15:51.200 --> 02:15:52.951
But a Mother Box...

1190
02:15:53.076 --> 02:15:55.454
turns smoke back into a house.

1191
02:16:01.293 --> 02:16:04.046
I know we're all thinking
the same thing right now.

1192
02:16:05.214 --> 02:16:08.008
Who's gonna say it?
I'm not gonna say it.

1193
02:16:35.035 --> 02:16:36.328
Who is it?

1194
02:16:36.912 --> 02:16:38.205
Martha.

1195
02:16:42.876 --> 02:16:44.211
Hi.

1196
02:16:45.963 --> 02:16:47.422
Hi.

1197
02:16:56.390 --> 02:16:57.975
I went to the<i> Daily Planet</i>

1198
02:16:58.100 --> 02:17:01.562
to finally pick up
Clark's things.

1199
02:17:02.980 --> 02:17:06.400
I don't know why.
nowhere to put them now.

1200
02:17:09.069 --> 02:17:10.904
I lost the farm.

1201
02:17:12.239 --> 02:17:14.491
I'd been behind on
the payments for a while.

1202
02:17:15.826 --> 02:17:17.202
Truth is. the house is too big

1203
02:17:17.327 --> 02:17:20.038
for me to live in
by myself anyway.

1204
02:17:20.163 --> 02:17:23.083
Well. you know you're welcome
to stay here any time

1205
02:17:23.166 --> 02:17:25.294
for as long as you need.

1206
02:17:26.253 --> 02:17:29.172
Thank you. Lois.
That's very kind.

1207
02:17:30.549 --> 02:17:32.843
But I've found a little place
that suits me just fine.

1208
02:17:32.968 --> 02:17:34.928
right by the diner.

1209
02:17:35.012 --> 02:17:36.430
I'm not here for help.

1210
02:17:37.598 --> 02:17:40.100
I'm here because

1211
02:17:40.225 --> 02:17:42.936
when I saw Mr. Perry.
he told me that

1212
02:17:44.146 --> 02:17:47.232
you haven't been to work
since Clark died.

1213
02:17:51.904 --> 02:17:53.572
I can't.

1214
02:18:00.329 --> 02:18:02.998
The whole world is mourning.

1215
02:18:04.291 --> 02:18:06.585
Grieving over a symbol.

1216
02:18:06.710 --> 02:18:10.964
Everywhere I go. everywhere
I look. I see that "S."

1217
02:18:11.882 --> 02:18:13.925
I hear what people say.

1218
02:18:14.009 --> 02:18:16.011
They talk like they knew him.

1219
02:18:17.012 --> 02:18:19.431
But they didn't know Clark.

1220
02:18:20.891 --> 02:18:23.185
And I can't stop them

1221
02:18:23.310 --> 02:18:27.689
and look at them and tell them
how proud I am of my son.

1222
02:18:29.733 --> 02:18:32.152
You're the only one who knows.

1223
02:18:32.277 --> 02:18:34.988
Who feels what I do.

1224
02:18:36.031 --> 02:18:39.201
Burdened by a secret
on top of grief.

1225
02:18:42.162 --> 02:18:45.666
I came all this way
because I wanted...

1226
02:18:45.749 --> 02:18:47.709
because I wanted to see you.

1227
02:18:48.961 --> 02:18:50.962
Tell you...

1228
02:18:51.004 --> 02:18:53.090
I understand.

1229
02:18:54.841 --> 02:18:56.802
I...

1230
02:18:56.927 --> 02:19:00.972
will never love anybody
the way that I love your son.

1231
02:19:04.601 --> 02:19:06.561
And I just miss him.

1232
02:19:07.729 --> 02:19:10.148
I miss him so much.

1233
02:19:16.697 --> 02:19:18.365
So do I. sweetheart.

1234
02:19:22.828 --> 02:19:27.708
Martha. you know if there's
anything you need. I'm here.

1235
02:19:31.211 --> 02:19:34.089
There is something
you can do for me. honey.

1236
02:19:36.258 --> 02:19:38.635
Come back to the living.

1237
02:20:18.425 --> 02:20:21.511
The world needs you. too. Lois.

1238
02:20:25.140 --> 02:20:26.475
<i>The dead are dead.</i>

1239
02:20:26.600 --> 02:20:28.602
The box brought Victor back.

1240
02:20:28.727 --> 02:20:30.187
Victor wasn't dead.

1241
02:20:30.312 --> 02:20:32.105
Life is either one or zero.

1242
02:20:32.230 --> 02:20:35.192
It's to be or not to be.
Not both.

1243
02:20:35.317 --> 02:20:36.943
Can you operate this box.
Victor?

1244
02:20:37.068 --> 02:20:38.361
Of course.

1245
02:20:38.487 --> 02:20:40.781
But we don't know enough
about Kryptonian biology.

1246
02:20:40.864 --> 02:20:43.116
There's no telling
what's gonna happen.

1247
02:20:44.701 --> 02:20:46.286
Okay. but...

1248
02:20:46.453 --> 02:20:50.749
I mean. we have to try.
Don't we? We have to try.

1249
02:20:50.791 --> 02:20:52.084
What do we have to lose?

1250
02:20:52.209 --> 02:20:54.669
We cannot try
unless we activate the box.

1251
02:20:54.795 --> 02:20:56.213
As soon as it wakes up...

1252
02:20:56.338 --> 02:20:58.799
the enemy sees it. comes.

1253
02:20:58.965 --> 02:21:01.426
activates The Unity.
The end.

1254
02:21:01.510 --> 02:21:03.845
So. what we have to lose
is the entire planet

1255
02:21:03.970 --> 02:21:06.139
{\an5}to a bunch of genocidal
aliens. That's good to know.

1256
02:21:06.264 --> 02:21:08.642
Even if Superman could return.

1257
02:21:08.809 --> 02:21:10.936
who's to say
that he could defeat them?

1258
02:21:11.019 --> 02:21:13.021
The Mother Box did.

1259
02:21:13.146 --> 02:21:15.315
Victor's father
activated a Mother Box

1260
02:21:15.440 --> 02:21:18.276
more than a year ago
when Superman was still alive.

1261
02:21:18.401 --> 02:21:20.320
Didn't call out to Steppenwolf.

1262
02:21:20.403 --> 02:21:21.988
None of the boxes did.
Not until...

1263
02:21:22.113 --> 02:21:24.157
Not until Superman died.

1264
02:21:24.324 --> 02:21:26.618
Not until Superman died.

1265
02:21:26.743 --> 02:21:28.703
It's like they were
afraid of him?

1266
02:21:28.829 --> 02:21:31.832
Yes. they were afraid of him.

1267
02:21:34.876 --> 02:21:36.670
This is the only way.

1268
02:21:38.004 --> 02:21:42.175
There are six. not five.
There is no us without him.

1269
02:21:58.358 --> 02:22:00.360
Cross this one off
the bucket list.

1270
02:22:00.443 --> 02:22:04.447
Exhume Superman
from the grave. Check.

1271
02:22:06.116 --> 02:22:08.827
You know we could do this
in a nanosecond. right?

1272
02:22:09.578 --> 02:22:10.871
We could.

1273
02:22:18.378 --> 02:22:20.213
He was my hero.

1274
02:22:22.757 --> 02:22:23.884
All right.

1275
02:22:27.429 --> 02:22:30.682
An Amazon
working with an Atlantean.

1276
02:22:30.765 --> 02:22:31.933
Half-Atlantean.

1277
02:22:33.727 --> 02:22:36.938
How many thousands of years
since our people spoke?

1278
02:22:37.063 --> 02:22:41.193
I don't know.
I'm not exactly close to mine.

1279
02:22:41.276 --> 02:22:44.112
I hate Atlanteans as much
as you Amazons do.

1280
02:22:44.237 --> 02:22:46.406
Hate is useless.

1281
02:22:49.576 --> 02:22:50.744
Yep.

1282
02:22:52.078 --> 02:22:53.705
No. thank you.

1283
02:22:58.126 --> 02:22:59.252
You know. my father told me

1284
02:22:59.377 --> 02:23:01.296
there's a saying in Atlantis...

1285
02:23:02.756 --> 02:23:05.050
"None are taken back
from the darkness.

1286
02:23:05.133 --> 02:23:06.343
"Not without..."

1287
02:23:06.468 --> 02:23:07.969
"Not without
giving one up in return."

1288
02:23:10.221 --> 02:23:11.806
We say the same thing.

1289
02:23:14.392 --> 02:23:16.144
How about that?

1290
02:23:16.269 --> 02:23:18.313
Wonder Woman.

1291
02:23:19.439 --> 02:23:20.732
What do you think. man?

1292
02:23:20.815 --> 02:23:23.610
You think she'd ever
go for a younger guy?

1293
02:23:23.735 --> 02:23:26.571
She's 5.000 years old. Barry.

1294
02:23:28.281 --> 02:23:30.325
Every guy's a younger guy.

1295
02:23:32.118 --> 02:23:33.203
Jesus.

1296
02:23:34.788 --> 02:23:36.581
Oh. Christ.

1297
02:23:38.833 --> 02:23:41.544
Oh. bloody...

1298
02:23:42.837 --> 02:23:43.922
Any luck?

1299
02:23:43.964 --> 02:23:45.340
If by "luck" you mean

1300
02:23:45.465 --> 02:23:48.259
"chance in hell
we'll get it flying today."

1301
02:23:48.385 --> 02:23:50.595
then. no. No luck.

1302
02:23:51.346 --> 02:23:52.806
It's okay.

1303
02:23:52.889 --> 02:23:54.849
It doesn't matter.
We're just gonna take the body

1304
02:23:54.975 --> 02:23:56.101
to the Kryptonian ship.

1305
02:23:56.226 --> 02:23:57.578
It's basically
an organic computer.

1306
02:23:57.602 --> 02:23:59.312
It can talk directly
to the Mother Box.

1307
02:23:59.479 --> 02:24:02.065
What? The way it talked
to Lex Luthor?

1308
02:24:02.190 --> 02:24:03.441
Something like that.

1309
02:24:03.566 --> 02:24:07.362
Huh.
What could possibly go wrong?

1310
02:24:13.868 --> 02:24:15.495
Master Wayne...

1311
02:24:17.372 --> 02:24:18.748
you did it!

1312
02:24:18.873 --> 02:24:22.419
You put the team together
to fight this war.

1313
02:24:22.544 --> 02:24:25.630
You've fulfilled your promise.

1314
02:24:25.714 --> 02:24:29.634
But to try to do that...
I mean...

1315
02:24:29.759 --> 02:24:32.679
your guilt's
overcome your reason.

1316
02:24:32.846 --> 02:24:34.973
Not all the king's horses
nor all the king's men...

1317
02:24:35.015 --> 02:24:38.351
{\an5}Alfred. for once.
I'm operating strictly on faith.

1318
02:24:38.476 --> 02:24:40.854
not on reason.

1319
02:24:40.979 --> 02:24:45.317
But if you start playing with
this little box of tricks.

1320
02:24:45.442 --> 02:24:47.569
I mean. it could be
the end of everything.

1321
02:24:47.694 --> 02:24:50.655
How do you know
your team's strong enough?

1322
02:24:50.739 --> 02:24:53.283
If you can't bring down
the charging bull.

1323
02:24:53.408 --> 02:24:55.201
then don't wave
the red cape at it.

1324
02:24:55.285 --> 02:24:56.995
You do when it's this red cape.

1325
02:24:57.078 --> 02:24:59.372
This red cape charges back.

1326
02:25:14.012 --> 02:25:15.096
Okay.

1327
02:25:21.936 --> 02:25:24.439
You were right. Dr. Stone.
The tests came back negative.

1328
02:25:24.564 --> 02:25:26.066
Everyone's clear. including you.

1329
02:25:26.232 --> 02:25:28.902
Just to be on the safe side.
we swept the entire facility.

1330
02:25:28.985 --> 02:25:30.963
Well. thank you. Thomas.
That means I'm free to go?

1331
02:25:30.987 --> 02:25:31.987
Absolutely.

1332
02:25:35.784 --> 02:25:37.035
- Thanks.
- Listen up. everyone.

1333
02:25:37.118 --> 02:25:39.746
You're all clear.
So. gather your things.

1334
02:25:39.871 --> 02:25:41.414
If you need
more medical attention...

1335
02:25:41.498 --> 02:25:45.418
Arthur. yes. your opinion.
Less preposterous. Option "A"?

1336
02:25:45.502 --> 02:25:46.920
- Definitely not "A."
- Okay.

1337
02:25:47.045 --> 02:25:50.090
Or... "B"?

1338
02:25:51.633 --> 02:25:53.009
Let me see "A" again?

1339
02:25:58.515 --> 02:26:01.810
Right. We should get dressed.

1340
02:26:03.770 --> 02:26:05.897
I'm always dressed.

1341
02:26:33.049 --> 02:26:34.134
ID?

1342
02:26:34.259 --> 02:26:35.552
ID.

1343
02:26:38.513 --> 02:26:39.806
Aye. aye.

1344
02:26:42.058 --> 02:26:43.434
"Aye. aye"?

1345
02:27:06.458 --> 02:27:07.709
Okay.

1346
02:27:07.834 --> 02:27:10.044
"Okay"? Oh. gee. okay!

1347
02:27:17.093 --> 02:27:18.011
Doc!

1348
02:27:18.094 --> 02:27:19.554
They let you out of quarantine.

1349
02:27:19.679 --> 02:27:21.198
Yeah. I finally got them
to listen to reason.

1350
02:27:21.222 --> 02:27:23.382
Now. let's take a look and see
what progress we've made

1351
02:27:23.475 --> 02:27:24.767
with the electron-laser.

1352
02:27:24.893 --> 02:27:27.020
We've made some real progress.
Let me show you.

1353
02:27:41.993 --> 02:27:44.954
Victor. clear this place out.

1354
02:27:45.079 --> 02:27:46.414
Done.

1355
02:27:50.210 --> 02:27:52.921
<i>Code Red.
Contamination breach.</i>

1356
02:27:53.046 --> 02:27:56.257
<i>All personnel
evacuate immediately.</i>

1357
02:27:56.382 --> 02:27:58.676
Bio red five.

1358
02:27:58.760 --> 02:28:01.137
The sensor's picking up
a microbe of alien origin.

1359
02:28:01.262 --> 02:28:04.182
A microbe of alien origin?
That doesn't make any sense.

1360
02:28:04.265 --> 02:28:05.516
It's gotta be a false alarm.

1361
02:28:05.642 --> 02:28:07.685
All right. people.
shut it down. Let's go.

1362
02:28:07.727 --> 02:28:09.205
- Ryan. we just had it swept.
- We have to go. Doc.

1363
02:28:09.229 --> 02:28:10.664
Think about it.
It's gotta be a false alarm.

1364
02:28:10.688 --> 02:28:12.023
- Let's go. Doc.
- Think about it.

1365
02:28:12.106 --> 02:28:13.209
Full base evacuation!
Everyone out!

1366
02:28:13.233 --> 02:28:15.318
Look. wait! Wait! Shit!

1367
02:28:15.443 --> 02:28:18.404
<i>Remain calm and
proceed to the nearest exit.</i>

1368
02:28:24.786 --> 02:28:26.579
<i>Attention. all personnel.</i>

1369
02:28:26.704 --> 02:28:29.582
Go! Go! Everybody out!
Come on! Move!

1370
02:28:29.666 --> 02:28:31.417
Move! Come on! Go. go!

1371
02:28:31.501 --> 02:28:33.086
Everybody out! Go!

1372
02:28:53.273 --> 02:28:56.067
Yes! Gotcha!

1373
02:28:56.192 --> 02:28:58.987
Post Commander. this is
Dr. Silas Stone. do you read?

1374
02:28:59.112 --> 02:29:01.489
- <i>Go ahead. Dr. Stone.</i>
- This is a false alarm.

1375
02:29:01.614 --> 02:29:04.409
Someone has hacked into
the system. We must alert...

1376
02:29:14.377 --> 02:29:15.878
Victor.

1377
02:29:17.338 --> 02:29:19.841
<i>Dr. Stone. you there?
I don't copy.</i>

1378
02:29:20.675 --> 02:29:21.759
I was mistaken.

1379
02:29:21.843 --> 02:29:23.052
The alarm's legit.

1380
02:29:23.177 --> 02:29:24.846
Everybody out.
And nobody. I repeat.

1381
02:29:24.971 --> 02:29:27.765
nobody comes back inside
without my say-so.

1382
02:29:27.849 --> 02:29:29.225
<i>Roger that. sir.</i>

1383
02:29:39.319 --> 02:29:40.987
Get the civilians out!

1384
02:29:41.112 --> 02:29:42.280
Let's go! Let's go!

1385
02:29:46.659 --> 02:29:47.928
- Everybody got out okay?
- I think so.

1386
02:29:47.952 --> 02:29:49.120
- Everybody?
- Yes.

1387
02:30:22.403 --> 02:30:23.780
This way.

1388
02:30:34.290 --> 02:30:37.043
It knows he's here.

1389
02:30:37.210 --> 02:30:39.337
Ooh. that's intense.

1390
02:30:43.716 --> 02:30:45.843
This is amazing.

1391
02:30:46.552 --> 02:30:47.720
This is crazy.

1392
02:30:47.845 --> 02:30:49.764
Oh. what? Now it's crazy?

1393
02:30:49.889 --> 02:30:52.350
You two lunatics
better know what you're doing.

1394
02:33:18.204 --> 02:33:20.206
<i>Systems coming online.</i>

1395
02:33:22.959 --> 02:33:25.253
<i>Welcome. Victor.</i>

1396
02:33:25.378 --> 02:33:27.296
<i>Would you like
to assume command?</i>

1397
02:33:27.421 --> 02:33:28.421
I'm in.

1398
02:33:37.557 --> 02:33:39.892
The ship says
the Mother Box is hostile.

1399
02:33:40.059 --> 02:33:41.602
I can override
the security protocols.

1400
02:33:41.727 --> 02:33:43.539
but there's no time to repair
all the electrical damage

1401
02:33:43.563 --> 02:33:44.939
that Luthor's
power surges caused

1402
02:33:45.064 --> 02:33:46.190
to the primary capacitors.

1403
02:33:46.274 --> 02:33:47.274
English.

1404
02:33:47.400 --> 02:33:49.902
There's not enough charge
to wake the box.

1405
02:33:50.027 --> 02:33:52.071
I might be able to do it.

1406
02:33:54.198 --> 02:33:56.158
I mean. I might be able
to jump-start it.

1407
02:33:56.284 --> 02:33:57.564
I don't like to break this rule.

1408
02:33:57.618 --> 02:33:59.412
but when I approach
the speed of light. I...

1409
02:33:59.495 --> 02:34:01.080
Look. crazy things
happen to time.

1410
02:34:01.247 --> 02:34:03.749
but if I do it. I create
massive electrical power.

1411
02:34:03.833 --> 02:34:05.713
I could backtrack.
if I can get enough distance.

1412
02:34:05.751 --> 02:34:08.087
I can conduct a significant
electrical current.

1413
02:34:08.254 --> 02:34:10.923
I might be able to wake
the box. if that's...

1414
02:34:11.048 --> 02:34:12.717
still what we want?

1415
02:34:12.800 --> 02:34:14.302
It is. Do it.

1416
02:34:19.056 --> 02:34:20.391
Hey. Miss Lane.

1417
02:34:20.474 --> 02:34:21.267
Morning.

1418
02:34:21.434 --> 02:34:22.935
I didn't think you were coming.

1419
02:34:23.853 --> 02:34:25.438
One last time.

1420
02:34:42.371 --> 02:34:46.125
I see engines. so this must be
the end of the line. So I'm...

1421
02:34:46.292 --> 02:34:47.460
<i>I'm in position.</i>

1422
02:34:50.212 --> 02:34:52.798
<i>- Ready to initiate
- Drop sequence.</i>

1423
02:34:52.882 --> 02:34:54.508
The Mother Box is ready.

1424
02:35:13.694 --> 02:35:15.613
The ship's begging me
not to wake the box.

1425
02:35:15.696 --> 02:35:17.615
<i>- This action
- Is irreversible.</i>

1426
02:35:17.698 --> 02:35:19.134
{\an5}It's afraid. It knows
Steppenwolf will come for it.

1427
02:35:19.158 --> 02:35:20.952
We know that already.
Continue.

1428
02:35:21.035 --> 02:35:23.663
<i>I strongly advise
against activation.</i>

1429
02:35:23.746 --> 02:35:25.414
Barry. I'm initiating
the countdown.

1430
02:35:25.539 --> 02:35:27.166
<i>- This action
- Is irreversible.</i>

1431
02:35:27.333 --> 02:35:28.459
- Five...
<i>- Five...</i>

1432
02:35:28.542 --> 02:35:29.961
- Five...
<i>- Apokoliptian technology</i>

1433
02:35:30.044 --> 02:35:31.188
<i>- is hostile.</i>
- This is a bad idea.

1434
02:35:31.212 --> 02:35:31.921
No. it isn't.
Keep going.

1435
02:35:32.046 --> 02:35:33.046
Four...

1436
02:35:33.172 --> 02:35:34.632
- <i>Four...</i>
- Four...

1437
02:35:34.757 --> 02:35:36.237
<i>I strongly advise
against activation.</i>

1438
02:35:36.300 --> 02:35:37.653
- We need to abort. now.
- Just do it.

1439
02:35:37.677 --> 02:35:38.803
- Three...
<i>- Three...</i>

1440
02:35:38.886 --> 02:35:39.887
Three...

1441
02:35:40.012 --> 02:35:41.722
- Two...
<i>- Two...</i>

1442
02:35:41.847 --> 02:35:43.766
- Two...
<i>- This course is irreversible.</i>

1443
02:35:43.891 --> 02:35:45.184
- One.
<i>- One.</i>

1444
02:35:46.018 --> 02:35:47.436
One.

1445
02:35:47.561 --> 02:35:48.854
<i>- This action
- Is irreversible.</i>

1446
02:37:17.860 --> 02:37:19.445
- <i>Victor?</i>
- No.

1447
02:37:20.446 --> 02:37:21.446
Go?

1448
02:38:51.912 --> 02:38:54.665
- <i>The future</i>
- has taken root in the present.

1449
02:38:54.790 --> 02:38:56.667
Get down!

1450
02:40:40.854 --> 02:40:42.439
He's back.

1451
02:41:09.091 --> 02:41:12.011
Something's wrong.
He's scanning us.

1452
02:41:14.179 --> 02:41:15.639
What?

1453
02:41:30.529 --> 02:41:31.697
Victor?

1454
02:41:32.906 --> 02:41:33.907
Victor?

1455
02:41:36.201 --> 02:41:38.078
- Shit.
- What are you doing?

1456
02:41:38.203 --> 02:41:39.830
It's my auto-defense system.

1457
02:41:39.913 --> 02:41:41.040
It senses danger.

1458
02:41:41.123 --> 02:41:42.374
Victor. no! Victor!

1459
02:41:42.499 --> 02:41:44.418
- I can't control it.
- Don't!

1460
02:41:56.597 --> 02:41:57.890
Kal-El. no!

1461
02:42:06.065 --> 02:42:08.359
He's confused.
He doesn't know who he is.

1462
02:42:15.365 --> 02:42:18.035
Arthur. we need to restrain him.

1463
02:42:48.482 --> 02:42:52.402
Kal-El.
the last Son of Krypton...

1464
02:42:53.320 --> 02:42:55.614
remember who you are.

1465
02:42:57.157 --> 02:42:58.408
Tell me who you...

1466
02:44:33.378 --> 02:44:36.548
Let's go!

1467
02:44:43.555 --> 02:44:45.015
You should probably move.

1468
02:44:48.518 --> 02:44:49.686
- You all right?
- Yeah.

1469
02:44:49.770 --> 02:44:52.564
Get up.
Take cover back there. Go.

1470
02:45:44.533 --> 02:45:46.743
Please don't make me do this.

1471
02:46:19.318 --> 02:46:20.652
Clark.

1472
02:46:21.528 --> 02:46:22.821
Clark. no.

1473
02:46:34.333 --> 02:46:35.542
Clark.

1474
02:46:35.667 --> 02:46:37.502
No.

1475
02:46:37.669 --> 02:46:39.379
This world needs you.

1476
02:46:44.634 --> 02:46:45.969
Clark.

1477
02:46:46.094 --> 02:46:47.179
Clark.

1478
02:46:47.262 --> 02:46:49.348
Whoa! Hold your fire!
Hold your fire!

1479
02:46:50.849 --> 02:46:52.142
Clark.

1480
02:46:55.520 --> 02:46:56.980
Please.

1481
02:47:31.223 --> 02:47:32.265
Please.

1482
02:47:43.443 --> 02:47:44.736
Please.

1483
02:47:45.404 --> 02:47:47.531
Just go.

1484
02:47:47.614 --> 02:47:48.782
Yeah.

1485
02:47:49.491 --> 02:47:50.909
Let's go.

1486
02:48:23.442 --> 02:48:25.610
I'm so sorry.

1487
02:48:34.828 --> 02:48:35.912
Take cover!

1488
02:48:35.954 --> 02:48:38.582
- He's coming.
- The Mother Box.

1489
02:48:38.623 --> 02:48:39.875
Where is it?

1490
02:48:50.427 --> 02:48:51.762
Come on.

1491
02:48:52.512 --> 02:48:54.347
Come on.

1492
02:49:19.039 --> 02:49:22.792
<i>Attention.
security breach detected.</i>

1493
02:49:22.918 --> 02:49:25.128
<i>Sector Four. Level Three.</i>

1494
02:49:25.212 --> 02:49:28.215
<i>Implement lockdown
procedures immediately.</i>

1495
02:49:56.701 --> 02:49:58.328
Give me the Mother Box.

1496
02:50:11.550 --> 02:50:13.051
No. no. no.

1497
02:50:15.512 --> 02:50:17.222
Dad. wait! Don't!

1498
02:50:57.512 --> 02:51:00.432
So begins the end.

1499
02:51:06.021 --> 02:51:07.439
Victor?

1500
02:51:09.733 --> 02:51:13.194
Vic... Whoa. Victor.
Are you okay. man? Come on.

1501
02:51:18.992 --> 02:51:20.327
Victor?

1502
02:51:21.494 --> 02:51:22.871
He's dead.

1503
02:51:22.996 --> 02:51:24.122
What?

1504
02:51:25.040 --> 02:51:26.374
My father.

1505
02:51:27.792 --> 02:51:31.254
I didn't save him. I couldn't.

1506
02:51:31.338 --> 02:51:32.964
Oh. my God.

1507
02:51:39.554 --> 02:51:41.598
His father's dead 'cause of us.

1508
02:51:41.723 --> 02:51:43.516
I told you waking that box
was a bad idea.

1509
02:51:43.642 --> 02:51:45.101
It wasn't a bad idea.

1510
02:51:45.226 --> 02:51:47.562
We needed Superman.
We still do.

1511
02:51:47.687 --> 02:51:50.148
{\an5}Well. whatever returned.
it isn't Superman.

1512
02:51:50.231 --> 02:51:53.485
His body and powers. maybe.
But it ain't him.

1513
02:51:53.568 --> 02:51:55.111
It is him.

1514
02:51:55.153 --> 02:51:57.656
He recognized Lois Lane.

1515
02:51:57.822 --> 02:51:59.950
- Who?
- The woman he loves.

1516
02:52:00.033 --> 02:52:02.327
- He remembers her.
- Nah.

1517
02:52:02.494 --> 02:52:04.334
He went to her 'cause
she wasn't afraid of him.

1518
02:52:04.412 --> 02:52:06.122
It's called instinct. Diana.

1519
02:52:13.296 --> 02:52:15.173
Wait. where did Steppenwolf go?

1520
02:52:15.298 --> 02:52:16.925
He's gone back to his base

1521
02:52:17.050 --> 02:52:18.593
to assemble the three boxes.

1522
02:52:18.718 --> 02:52:20.178
And we don't know
where his base is.

1523
02:52:20.345 --> 02:52:22.013
- Or how long until...
- Hours.

1524
02:52:22.097 --> 02:52:23.682
The boxes synchronize.
Unity forms.

1525
02:52:23.765 --> 02:52:27.018
we don't get there in time
to stop it. the planet dies.

1526
02:52:27.102 --> 02:52:29.312
This is not your...

1527
02:52:31.481 --> 02:52:32.982
He knew.

1528
02:52:33.066 --> 02:52:34.609
He knew. he knew. he knew.

1529
02:52:34.734 --> 02:52:36.695
He wasn't trying
to destroy the box...

1530
02:52:36.778 --> 02:52:38.738
he was trying to superheat it.

1531
02:52:38.863 --> 02:52:40.183
He made the core
the hottest thing

1532
02:52:40.240 --> 02:52:41.467
on Earth outside
of a nuclear reactor.

1533
02:52:41.491 --> 02:52:42.551
Now. anything that hot
would have to...

1534
02:52:42.575 --> 02:52:43.785
Blink off the charts

1535
02:52:43.910 --> 02:52:46.037
on a thermal imaging system.

1536
02:52:46.204 --> 02:52:49.499
Your father sacrificed himself
to mark that box.

1537
02:52:49.582 --> 02:52:51.582
We have to get back to my lab
and use the satellite

1538
02:52:51.668 --> 02:52:53.837
to scan the Earth
for thermal anomalies.

1539
02:52:53.962 --> 02:52:55.338
I'm already on it.

1540
02:52:55.422 --> 02:52:57.424
I'm sorry.
You have a satellite?

1541
02:52:57.549 --> 02:52:58.842
I have six.

1542
02:52:58.925 --> 02:53:00.176
Right.

1543
02:53:01.594 --> 02:53:04.014
Let's go find
the son of a bitch.

1544
02:53:28.288 --> 02:53:30.540
You brought us here.

1545
02:53:30.665 --> 02:53:31.791
You remembered.

1546
02:53:32.751 --> 02:53:34.419
This is home.

1547
02:53:36.171 --> 02:53:37.547
You spoke.

1548
02:53:41.593 --> 02:53:43.470
Did I not before?

1549
02:54:17.337 --> 02:54:20.131
Your mother got behind
on the payments.

1550
02:54:21.341 --> 02:54:23.510
She never told anyone.

1551
02:54:25.053 --> 02:54:26.846
I don't understand.

1552
02:54:29.974 --> 02:54:32.477
She's a proud woman. Clark.

1553
02:54:35.605 --> 02:54:36.856
Here.

1554
02:54:51.871 --> 02:54:53.540
She loved it here.

1555
02:55:04.217 --> 02:55:05.885
So did I.

1556
02:55:07.887 --> 02:55:09.430
So did I.

1557
02:55:34.998 --> 02:55:36.249
Wow!

1558
02:55:36.374 --> 02:55:38.042
This is awesome.

1559
02:55:38.209 --> 02:55:39.752
Brought some friends.

1560
02:55:46.259 --> 02:55:48.720
Oh. gosh. yes! Yes!

1561
02:55:48.845 --> 02:55:51.472
Everyone. this is Alfred.
I work for him.

1562
02:55:51.598 --> 02:55:53.892
- Alfred.
- Good day. ma'am.

1563
02:55:55.184 --> 02:55:57.353
Oh...

1564
02:56:00.315 --> 02:56:02.400
It's badass. Alfred.

1565
02:56:05.069 --> 02:56:07.614
Well. I'll put on the tea.

1566
02:56:07.739 --> 02:56:08.865
Great.

1567
02:56:08.990 --> 02:56:10.750
I don't know where
we're gonna find the cups.

1568
02:56:13.411 --> 02:56:16.372
There's the
Mother Box. right there.

1569
02:56:16.414 --> 02:56:18.458
Go to visible spectrum.

1570
02:56:20.293 --> 02:56:22.420
Pozharnov.

1571
02:56:22.545 --> 02:56:25.423
Ghost city not far from Moscow.

1572
02:56:25.548 --> 02:56:26.799
It's been abandoned since

1573
02:56:26.925 --> 02:56:28.402
the nuclear accident there
30 years ago.

1574
02:56:28.426 --> 02:56:29.719
Not even the army goes in.

1575
02:56:29.802 --> 02:56:31.220
Right. it's probably
so radioactive

1576
02:56:31.346 --> 02:56:33.389
that you grow an extra foot
outta your neck.

1577
02:56:33.431 --> 02:56:34.849
Not anymore.

1578
02:56:34.974 --> 02:56:36.785
He's harvested the radiation
to build his base.

1579
02:56:36.809 --> 02:56:37.852
Zoom.

1580
02:56:41.689 --> 02:56:43.232
What the hell is he building?

1581
02:56:43.316 --> 02:56:44.776
The Unity's in there.

1582
02:56:44.859 --> 02:56:46.236
We'll attack from above.

1583
02:56:46.319 --> 02:56:49.030
Explosives won't
separate the boxes.

1584
02:56:49.155 --> 02:56:50.782
only strengthen their bond.

1585
02:56:50.949 --> 02:56:52.283
What?
So we can't blow it up?

1586
02:56:52.367 --> 02:56:53.910
Not from the outside.

1587
02:56:55.411 --> 02:56:58.331
I want to plug into
The Unity. one-on-one.

1588
02:56:58.456 --> 02:56:59.832
Fuse with it.

1589
02:56:59.958 --> 02:57:01.292
Weaken its bond from the inside

1590
02:57:01.459 --> 02:57:02.811
so we can break it back
into three.

1591
02:57:02.835 --> 02:57:04.921
No. you don't know
what you'd be up against.

1592
02:57:04.963 --> 02:57:08.675
You'd have to stream
into The Unity by yourself.

1593
02:57:08.800 --> 02:57:11.302
These boxes together
are world destroyers.

1594
02:57:11.386 --> 02:57:12.762
A billion years old.

1595
02:57:12.845 --> 02:57:14.931
They'll get inside you
and find your weaknesses

1596
02:57:15.056 --> 02:57:17.475
and your fears.
and use them to destroy you.

1597
02:57:17.558 --> 02:57:19.811
Just get me in and get me time.

1598
02:57:19.978 --> 02:57:21.104
You could die. Victor.

1599
02:57:21.187 --> 02:57:23.648
If I don't. we all die.
Period.

1600
02:57:28.236 --> 02:57:30.029
I got nothing left.

1601
02:57:35.326 --> 02:57:37.495
You wanted me
to use these gifts. right?

1602
02:57:40.415 --> 02:57:42.000
That's what I'm gonna do.

1603
02:57:42.166 --> 02:57:44.502
Okay. So...

1604
02:57:44.627 --> 02:57:46.295
if Victor wants
to try to save the world

1605
02:57:46.337 --> 02:57:47.880
by fusing with the doom boxes.

1606
02:57:48.006 --> 02:57:50.508
I say we put him
in the doom boxes.

1607
02:57:50.591 --> 02:57:53.469
But getting him in
means attacking that base.

1608
02:57:53.511 --> 02:57:55.972
Fighting the devil and his army

1609
02:57:56.055 --> 02:57:57.307
in hell.

1610
02:57:57.432 --> 02:57:59.475
I mean.
this guy's probably fought

1611
02:57:59.559 --> 02:58:01.811
hundreds of thousands
of other superbeings

1612
02:58:01.894 --> 02:58:03.574
on the other planets
he's destroyed. right?

1613
02:58:03.688 --> 02:58:05.315
And we have to assume he's won.

1614
02:58:05.356 --> 02:58:07.108
I don't care
how many demons he's fought

1615
02:58:07.233 --> 02:58:08.526
in how many hells...

1616
02:58:08.651 --> 02:58:12.363
he's never fought us.
Not us united.

1617
02:59:02.622 --> 02:59:04.290
Take that as a "yes."

1618
02:59:04.415 --> 02:59:05.875
What?

1619
02:59:09.295 --> 02:59:10.588
The ring.

1620
02:59:14.258 --> 02:59:15.843
You're really back.

1621
02:59:49.293 --> 02:59:51.629
I have a second chance. Lo.

1622
02:59:53.673 --> 02:59:56.425
And I am not gonna waste it.

1623
03:00:54.442 --> 03:00:55.651
Are you really you?

1624
03:00:55.735 --> 03:00:58.154
I'm really me. Ma.

1625
03:01:15.546 --> 03:01:17.715
Listen. Ma.

1626
03:01:19.050 --> 03:01:21.219
They wanted me back
for a reason.

1627
03:01:22.887 --> 03:01:24.680
I need to find out why.

1628
03:01:44.617 --> 03:01:46.118
How's Victor doing?

1629
03:01:50.414 --> 03:01:53.251
You know.
wanted to be by himself.

1630
03:01:54.752 --> 03:01:57.880
We're asking a kid
who just lost his father

1631
03:01:57.964 --> 03:01:59.608
to go up against
the most powerful machines

1632
03:01:59.632 --> 03:02:01.008
in the universe.

1633
03:02:02.718 --> 03:02:04.262
It's not fair.

1634
03:02:05.930 --> 03:02:07.765
I thought you didn't care?

1635
03:02:09.141 --> 03:02:10.726
I never said that.

1636
03:02:23.489 --> 03:02:24.991
What is it?

1637
03:02:26.617 --> 03:02:28.661
Uh...

1638
03:02:28.786 --> 03:02:31.872
I had a dream.
like. I don't know.

1639
03:02:31.998 --> 03:02:34.584
almost like a premonition.

1640
03:02:34.709 --> 03:02:37.586
It was the end of the world

1641
03:02:37.670 --> 03:02:40.589
and Barry Allen was right here

1642
03:02:40.673 --> 03:02:44.802
and he said to me.
"Lois Lane is the key."

1643
03:02:47.346 --> 03:02:50.683
She is... to Superman.

1644
03:02:51.559 --> 03:02:53.603
Every heart has one.

1645
03:02:53.728 --> 03:02:55.813
I think it's something more.

1646
03:02:56.522 --> 03:02:58.649
Something darker.

1647
03:03:02.612 --> 03:03:03.613
Master Wayne.

1648
03:03:03.696 --> 03:03:05.865
Master Wayne!

1649
03:03:05.990 --> 03:03:07.908
You need to see this.

1650
03:03:31.182 --> 03:03:32.767
You fixed it.

1651
03:03:32.892 --> 03:03:34.810
It wanted to fly.

1652
03:03:35.853 --> 03:03:37.355
Flight is its nature.

1653
03:03:37.438 --> 03:03:38.856
Yours. too.

1654
03:03:45.321 --> 03:03:47.490
He'll be here. Alfred.
I know it.

1655
03:03:47.573 --> 03:03:49.825
What makes you so sure?

1656
03:03:49.867 --> 03:03:52.745
Faith. Alfred. Faith.

1657
03:04:14.684 --> 03:04:16.310
At last.

1658
03:04:18.020 --> 03:04:20.940
Prepare for his arrival.

1659
03:04:22.650 --> 03:04:26.904
My redemption is nigh.

1660
03:04:34.620 --> 03:04:36.205
Unite.

1661
03:04:41.377 --> 03:04:43.921
Synchronize.

1662
03:05:28.007 --> 03:05:29.467
The satellites revealed

1663
03:05:29.550 --> 03:05:30.968
he's created a defensive dome.

1664
03:05:31.135 --> 03:05:32.344
It's a design flaw.

1665
03:05:32.470 --> 03:05:34.638
Take out the tower.
the dome will fall.

1666
03:05:34.722 --> 03:05:36.932
The enemy never anticipated
a frontal assault.

1667
03:05:37.016 --> 03:05:38.601
Right. probably
'cause he didn't think

1668
03:05:38.684 --> 03:05:40.811
anyone would be that nuts.

1669
03:05:41.645 --> 03:05:42.938
Bruce is right.

1670
03:05:42.980 --> 03:05:44.500
We've got to destroy
the defensive dome

1671
03:05:44.648 --> 03:05:47.109
so we can reach The Unity
before it synchronizes.

1672
03:05:47.193 --> 03:05:48.986
What if the dome's
not destroyed?

1673
03:05:49.111 --> 03:05:50.488
It'll be destroyed.

1674
03:05:50.571 --> 03:05:52.448
Once Victor
is linked with The Unity

1675
03:05:52.531 --> 03:05:53.783
with Barry's help.

1676
03:05:53.908 --> 03:05:55.784
he'll break through
The Unity's defenses.

1677
03:05:55.868 --> 03:05:57.495
Remind me. how's that again?

1678
03:05:57.578 --> 03:05:58.996
Uh. with the power of love.

1679
03:05:59.163 --> 03:06:02.124
{\an5}- Barry.
- With a catastrophic
energy surge.

1680
03:06:02.208 --> 03:06:03.459
Good.

1681
03:06:03.626 --> 03:06:05.395
You'll have to run faster
than you've ever attempted

1682
03:06:05.419 --> 03:06:07.838
to generate
a charge of that size.

1683
03:06:08.005 --> 03:06:10.174
And then you make
physical contact with Victor.

1684
03:06:10.257 --> 03:06:13.135
That force should propel him
inside The Unity.

1685
03:06:13.260 --> 03:06:15.221
And. Victor. it's all up to you.

1686
03:06:15.346 --> 03:06:18.557
Take it apart from the inside
before it synchronizes.

1687
03:06:18.682 --> 03:06:22.394
Whew. We actually
finally have a plan.

1688
03:06:22.520 --> 03:06:24.271
We have a plan.

1689
03:06:39.370 --> 03:06:41.455
<i>The symbol</i>
of the house of El means hope.

1690
03:06:41.580 --> 03:06:43.707
<i>Embodied within that hope
is the fundamental belief</i>

1691
03:06:43.833 --> 03:06:45.835
<i>in the potential of every</i>

1692
03:06:45.836 --> 03:06:47.836
person to be a force for good.

1693
03:06:47.920 --> 03:06:49.338
<i>Clark...</i>

1694
03:06:49.421 --> 03:06:51.048
<i>That's what you can bring them.</i>

1695
03:06:51.173 --> 03:06:52.573
<i>You were sent here for a reason.</i>

1696
03:06:52.716 --> 03:06:54.301
<i>You will give
the people of Earth</i>

1697
03:06:54.426 --> 03:06:56.470
<i>an ideal to strive towards.</i>

1698
03:06:56.595 --> 03:06:57.721
<i>And even if it takes you</i>

1699
03:06:57.888 --> 03:06:59.515
<i>the rest of your life.</i>

1700
03:06:59.598 --> 03:07:01.142
<i>you owe it to yourself to</i>

1701
03:07:01.143 --> 03:07:02.685
<i>find out what that reason is.</i>

1702
03:07:02.768 --> 03:07:05.521
<i>They will stumble.
they will fall.</i>

1703
03:07:05.604 --> 03:07:07.565
<i>- You're gonna
- Have to make a choice.</i>

1704
03:07:07.731 --> 03:07:10.234
<i>- They will join you
- In the sun. Kal.</i>

1705
03:07:10.401 --> 03:07:12.236
<i>A choice
of whether to stand proud</i>

1706
03:07:12.403 --> 03:07:14.363
<i>in front of the human race
or not.</i>

1707
03:07:14.446 --> 03:07:17.992
<i>You will help them
accomplish wonders.</i>

1708
03:07:34.758 --> 03:07:39.388
<i>All the hopes and dreams
of Krypton live in you now.</i>

1709
03:07:39.430 --> 03:07:43.058
<i>I'm so proud of you. son.</i>

1710
03:07:43.100 --> 03:07:45.811
<i>Your mother and I loved you.</i>

1711
03:07:45.936 --> 03:07:47.271
<i>Your mother and I knew</i>

1712
03:07:47.354 --> 03:07:49.523
<i>you would change the world.</i>

1713
03:07:50.816 --> 03:07:53.569
<i>Your heart was tested.</i>

1714
03:07:53.652 --> 03:07:56.363
<i>I know it's been hard. Clark.</i>

1715
03:07:56.488 --> 03:07:59.450
<i>But you gave hope
to their world.</i>

1716
03:07:59.533 --> 03:08:02.911
<i>You need
to show them who you are.</i>

1717
03:08:02.995 --> 03:08:05.164
<i>Love them. Kal.</i>

1718
03:08:05.289 --> 03:08:07.583
<i>The way we loved you.</i>

1719
03:08:10.002 --> 03:08:11.253
<i>Fly. son.</i>

1720
03:08:12.129 --> 03:08:13.464
<i>It's time.</i>

1721
03:09:17.111 --> 03:09:18.404
I'm gonna take out that tower

1722
03:09:18.529 --> 03:09:20.447
and knock down that shield dome.

1723
03:09:20.572 --> 03:09:21.615
Whatever you see.

1724
03:09:22.908 --> 03:09:25.035
stick to the plan.

1725
03:09:26.537 --> 03:09:28.706
It's why I brought you together.

1726
03:10:08.579 --> 03:10:10.581
Bruce. pull back.
You're not gonna make it.

1727
03:10:13.459 --> 03:10:16.420
Just have to knock
a little louder.

1728
03:10:41.487 --> 03:10:42.946
Kill him!

1729
03:10:43.071 --> 03:10:45.824
Get to the carriage.
Defend The Unity.

1730
03:10:50.788 --> 03:10:52.080
Oh. shit.

1731
03:11:12.017 --> 03:11:13.393
The tower's down.

1732
03:11:14.937 --> 03:11:16.855
Do you read me?

1733
03:11:16.980 --> 03:11:18.232
Uh. yeah. loud and clear.

1734
03:11:19.149 --> 03:11:20.609
<i>Are you okay?</i>

1735
03:11:21.819 --> 03:11:24.655
<i>Bruce? Bruce?</i>

1736
03:11:24.738 --> 03:11:25.614
Get to the reactor.

1737
03:11:25.697 --> 03:11:27.199
I'll lure as many
of these monsters

1738
03:11:27.324 --> 03:11:29.326
- away from you as I can.
- What does that mean?

1739
03:11:32.204 --> 03:11:34.164
Don't worry about me.
Get to The Unity.

1740
03:11:36.917 --> 03:11:38.001
They're here.

1741
03:11:38.085 --> 03:11:39.336
<i>Bruce?</i>

1742
03:11:42.172 --> 03:11:43.632
Comm went dead.

1743
03:11:45.217 --> 03:11:46.593
Let's go.

1744
03:12:25.382 --> 03:12:27.384
Come on. follow me.
you damn insects.

1745
03:13:47.005 --> 03:13:48.507
<i>Critical damage.</i>

1746
03:14:28.380 --> 03:14:29.715
You really are outta your mind.

1747
03:14:56.491 --> 03:14:57.826
You're welcome.

1748
03:14:57.909 --> 03:14:59.453
My man.

1749
03:16:32.212 --> 03:16:33.964
Yeah. we got this.

1750
03:16:34.089 --> 03:16:35.298
You go do your thing.

1751
03:17:31.229 --> 03:17:32.814
I'm assuming you're Alfred.

1752
03:17:34.566 --> 03:17:35.942
Master Kent.

1753
03:17:37.777 --> 03:17:39.571
He said you'd come.

1754
03:17:40.947 --> 03:17:44.701
Now. let's hope
you're not too late.

1755
03:17:55.420 --> 03:17:57.797
Hey!

1756
03:18:05.722 --> 03:18:07.140
Remember me?

1757
03:18:09.601 --> 03:18:11.102
Round two?

1758
03:18:11.728 --> 03:18:13.021
Hell yeah.

1759
03:18:34.459 --> 03:18:35.919
Shall we?

1760
03:18:36.753 --> 03:18:39.005
Tell me. Amazon.

1761
03:18:39.130 --> 03:18:43.176
why did you
abandon your own sisters

1762
03:18:43.301 --> 03:18:45.887
only to cast your lot
with these creatures

1763
03:18:45.971 --> 03:18:49.432
clinging to their puny lives?

1764
03:18:49.558 --> 03:18:52.519
You weren't there
to protect them from me.

1765
03:18:52.644 --> 03:18:54.562
And. sadly. you could have.

1766
03:19:35.645 --> 03:19:37.355
Barry. I'm in position.

1767
03:19:56.041 --> 03:19:59.377
Okay.
I built the charge.

1768
03:19:59.502 --> 03:20:00.502
<i>You call it.</i>

1769
03:20:01.671 --> 03:20:03.506
Barry. on one.

1770
03:20:03.631 --> 03:20:05.842
Three. two...

1771
03:20:08.720 --> 03:20:10.472
Get the hell off me!

1772
03:20:10.597 --> 03:20:12.057
Victor!

1773
03:20:48.134 --> 03:20:49.761
Victor!

1774
03:20:53.473 --> 03:20:55.850
I watched your island burn.

1775
03:20:55.975 --> 03:20:59.562
your sisters
begging for their lives.

1776
03:20:59.729 --> 03:21:02.315
As did your mother.

1777
03:21:02.440 --> 03:21:03.440
Liar.

1778
03:21:29.008 --> 03:21:31.177
I can't maintain this!

1779
03:21:31.928 --> 03:21:33.096
Victor!

1780
03:21:55.118 --> 03:21:57.454
Victor. I can't hold this!

1781
03:22:03.960 --> 03:22:06.379
For Darkseid.

1782
03:22:10.383 --> 03:22:12.844
Not impressed.

1783
03:22:57.263 --> 03:22:58.431
All right.

1784
03:22:58.556 --> 03:23:00.183
Kal-El.

1785
03:23:38.429 --> 03:23:40.848
Barry. I'm connected
to The Unity.

1786
03:23:40.890 --> 03:23:43.059
I need the charge to get inside.

1787
03:24:04.914 --> 03:24:06.124
Barry?

1788
03:24:06.916 --> 03:24:08.710
Barry. are you okay?

1789
03:24:10.128 --> 03:24:11.212
<i>Barry!</i>

1790
03:24:11.337 --> 03:24:12.606
I got the wind
knocked out of me.

1791
03:24:12.630 --> 03:24:15.383
Need a few seconds. that's all!

1792
03:24:32.275 --> 03:24:34.819
Barry. where are you?
It's almost synchronized!

1793
03:24:34.944 --> 03:24:36.946
Okay. okay.

1794
03:24:37.071 --> 03:24:39.782
Oh. my God. Gotta heal. Barry.

1795
03:24:39.908 --> 03:24:41.618
Heal. Heal.

1796
03:25:07.477 --> 03:25:09.145
Barry!

1797
03:25:21.908 --> 03:25:23.660
It's too late.

1798
03:25:24.911 --> 03:25:26.454
Oh. no.

1799
03:25:30.667 --> 03:25:32.335
He's here!

1800
03:26:01.739 --> 03:26:02.990
Okay.

1801
03:26:03.116 --> 03:26:04.218
Just gotta go faster
than the speed of light.

1802
03:26:04.242 --> 03:26:05.344
Far beyond the speed of light.

1803
03:26:05.368 --> 03:26:06.648
You gotta break the rule. Barry.

1804
03:26:06.703 --> 03:26:08.746
and you gotta do it now.

1805
03:26:21.843 --> 03:26:23.553
Dad...

1806
03:26:27.265 --> 03:26:29.726
whatever happens.
I want you to know

1807
03:26:32.311 --> 03:26:34.480
your kid was one of them. Dad.

1808
03:26:37.442 --> 03:26:39.569
One of the best of the best.

1809
03:27:34.999 --> 03:27:37.585
Make your own future.

1810
03:27:44.008 --> 03:27:46.135
Make your own past.

1811
03:27:50.389 --> 03:27:54.227
It's all right now.

1812
03:28:41.065 --> 03:28:43.401
We've been waiting
for you. Victor.

1813
03:28:44.360 --> 03:28:46.571
My broken boy.

1814
03:28:48.739 --> 03:28:50.992
You don't have to be
alone anymore.

1815
03:28:51.033 --> 03:28:52.785
We'll be together again.

1816
03:29:00.459 --> 03:29:02.712
We can put it back. Vic.

1817
03:29:07.049 --> 03:29:09.302
Make you whole again.

1818
03:29:21.022 --> 03:29:22.773
I'm not broken.

1819
03:29:32.408 --> 03:29:34.452
And I'm not alone.

1820
03:29:51.135 --> 03:29:52.303
Superman!

1821
03:31:22.893 --> 03:31:24.854
I told you

1822
03:31:26.355 --> 03:31:29.025
Steppenwolf would fail.

1823
03:31:30.026 --> 03:31:33.696
Yes. Yes. you did.

1824
03:31:34.280 --> 03:31:35.573
My master.

1825
03:31:35.698 --> 03:31:39.493
now that the Mother Boxes
have been destroyed.

1826
03:31:39.535 --> 03:31:43.497
